name: OB_HSB_FLUID_ODOR
description: This table contains information about the fluid odor from the rupture of membranes during the delivery for this pregnancy.

columns.name: SUMMARY_BLOCK_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the summary block record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: FLUID_ODOR_C_NAME
columns.description: Stores the odor associated with the fluid from the membrane rupture during a delivery.
